  "response": "There are several reputable solar panel installation providers in San Dimas, California. Here are a few you might consider:\n\n1. **Verengo Solar** - Known for good customer service and financing options. They have a strong presence in California.\n\n2. **Sunrun** - One of the largest residential solar providers in the U.S., offering various financing options, including leases and power purchase agreements.\n\n3. **Sunnova** - Offers customizable solar solutions with flexible payment options and has a good reputation for customer service.\n\n4. **Tesla Solar** - Provides solar panels and energy storage solutions, known for their innovative technology and high efficiency.\n\n5. **Freedom Forever** - Provides a lifetime warranty on their installations and is known for good customer service and a transparent process.\n\nIt's a good idea to get multiple quotes and check customer reviews to find the provider that best meets your needs. Additionally, ensure that they are licensed and insured for solar installations in California.",
